    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The issue is maybe a documentation issue because even if it worked, we do not document anymore to use transformData: function(){}. It's either transformData.hits or transformData.empty (no results).\n\nWe could also just throw when we have a transformData: function() {} passed.\n",
