  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "`transformData: () => {}` is a shortcut to `transformData: { hits: () => {} }`\n\nRemoving support for the shortcut notation will surely break a lot of implementations (starting with our own demos and tutorials). I think it needs to be better explained in the documentation, but not removed.\n",
